Ryan's devastated friends and loved ones have written tribute messages on Facebook, while his girlfriend Jaime-Leigh Egerton posted two poignant pictures of the pair together - including one of them sharing a tender kiss.

The dark-haired 20-year-old states on her Facebook profile that she works in high street retailer New Look and bar chain Yates.

Friends posted tributes on social networking sites as news of the tragedy spread.

Ryan's pal Adam Wicks wrote on Facebook: 'Words cant even explain what you ment to me Ryan Harrison i'll miss you so much, truly lost a brother. nothing will even be the same now. love you and sleep tight xxxx'.

